                "invention-title": [
                    "Device and method for high-sensitivity measurement of hydrogen chloride by non-radioactive ionization source ion mobility spectrometry",
                    "一种非放射性电离源离子迁移谱高灵敏测量氯化氢的装置及方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention discloses a device and a method for high-sensitivity measurement of hydrogen chloride in an atmospheric environment by VUV lamp-ion mobility spectrometry. On the basis of the anion mode ion mobility spectrometry, a novel vacuum ultraviolet (VUV) lamp ionization source is adopted, reagent ions are generated in carrier gas of the IMS by assisting reagent molecules such as acetone and one doping agent in organic compounds with ionization energy smaller than 10.04 ev, then the reagent ions react with hydrogen chloride in a sample to generate chloride ions, and finally the ions enter an ion migration tube, so that the ion mobility spectrometry is realized. Separating in a uniform electric field, and detecting after reaching a Faraday disc in a migration tube in sequence. On the basis of a VUV-ion migration method, online monitoring of HCl is realized, the method has the remarkable advantages of high resolution, high sensitivity and real-time monitoring, the content of hydrogen chloride in different environments can be detected, the response speed is high, and the method has a wide application prospect in real-time online detection of the content of hydrogen chloride in air."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明公开了一种VUV灯‑离子迁移谱高灵敏测量大气环境中氯化氢装置及方法。本发明基于负离子模式离子迁移谱，采用新型真空紫外(VUV)灯电离源，在IMS的载气中辅助试剂分子丙酮等电离能小于10.04ev的有机化合物中的一种掺杂剂生成试剂离子，然后与样品中的氯化氢反应生成氯离子，最后这些离子进入离子迁移管，在均匀电场中进行分离，先后到达迁移管中的法拉第盘得以检测。本方法基于一种VUV‑离子迁移法实现对HCl的在线监测，呈现出高分辨、高灵敏、实时监测的显著优点，可检测出不同环境中氯化氢的含量，响应速度快，对实时在线检测空气中的氯化氢含量具有广阔的应用前景。"
                }
            ]
